rows.label: qst700604_msg0004
rows.name:
A smokescreen for attracting bugs.
Weren't you listening?

rows.label: qst700604_msg0005
rows.name:
Ugh... I'm not sure I approve of
the smell...

rows.label: qst700604_msg0006
rows.name: Whoa, what's with all the monsters?

rows.label: qst700604_msg0007
rows.name:
Hmm. I suppose we can conclude
that the smoke is more effective in
attracting monsters than bugs.

rows.label: qst700604_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh, that's just great. Stupid piece
of junk! More trouble than it's worth...

rows.label: qst700604_msg0009
rows.name:
Guys, we can moan about this later.
Kind of got more pressing matters here!
